给定初始海拔高度,遍历数组计算出每次的海报高度

```
var largestAltitude = function(gain) {
  return Math.max(...gain.reduce((acc,cur) => {
    acc.push(acc[acc.length - 1] + cur);
    return acc
  },[0]))
};

```
